text: Niall Scully (born 19 April 1994) is a Gaelic footballer who plays for the Templeogue Synge Street club and for the Dublin county team. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Dublin inter-county Gaelic footballers Category:Gaelic football forwards Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city) Category:Templeogue Synge St. Gaelic footballers
